# MSNC PeopleHub — Rules Dokumen

## Struktur LOCK

- **Root** — hanya fail wajib npm/Next + README.md pendek
- **panduan/** — SEMUA txt dokumentasi
- **config-projek/** — JSON config sistem (manifest, auth-defaults, app-settings)
- **config-tetapan/** — URL host, deploy info
- **docs/** — docx rujukan sahaja
- **src/** — kod sahaja
- **launcher/** — .bat | **deploy/** — production scripts

## Fail JSON

- Config & data seed → **config-projek/**
- Root JSON (package.json, tsconfig.json) — wajib npm/Next, **jangan pindah**

## Larangan

- Jangan cipta txt di root — guna **panduan/**
- Jangan cipta txt dalam src/

## Rujukan wajib

1. panduan/PANDUAN-DEPLOY.txt
2. panduan/Daily Task.txt
3. config-projek/manifest-fail-penting.json

## Komunikasi

- Melayu dengan abang | English dalam kod/UI
- **WAJIB:** selepas coding baru, pastikan `npm run dev` / `localhost:3000` **UP**
  (check port 3000; start dev server jika mati — abang tak perlu start manual)
- Phase 2 / SQL / deploy hanya bila user minta explicitly